The '''Republic Classic era''' was the period of [[Timeline of galactic history/Legends|galactic history]] immediately preceding the waning [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. [[Bail Prestor Organa/Legends|Bail Prestor Organa]] always meticulously dressed in the [[Republic Classic era style]], like the [[Naboo (people)/Legends|Naboo]], as opposed to the ostentatious clothing such as the fashion of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="DL">''[[Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader]]''</ref>

